{"tid":1389169,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉推]【分析】天水圍放煙花係一場傑出PR","createTime":"2019-07-30T23:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T00:56:40.000Z","uid":8841,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a015fb388b1ba892fc9a8420b2b58778498a810","tid":1389169,"uid":8841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:56:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由千夫所指到主持大局</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">抗議者包圍警署，原本警察只能被動地被圍屌。但當外面馬路突然放煙花，然後即刻有個外表上鏡、似足TVB警察劇主角既藍衫出黎講野，呼籲救人要緊。<br />\n放煙花之後，抗議者由抗議警察執法不公，變成市民尋求警察保護。<span style=\"color: red;\">放煙花之後，現場由抗議警權，係「救人要緊」既大旗下，急速逆轉成由警察「主持大局」，甚至因此得到掌聲。</span>「執法不公」、拘捕學生時「濫用暴力」、「警黑合作」完全被放埋一邊。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時間天衣無縫</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">放煙花時間，剛好安排在3位學生被釋放之後數分鐘；「驅散人群」的觀感大減，始終釋放學生就，追究執法不公的關注度就會降低。然後一放煙花，「救人要緊」就自然完全蓋過追究執法不公。<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一洗落閘「唔做野」形象</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">天水圍警署比人屌得最勁，就係7.21落閘唔做野。但今次一反常態地，幾個警察即刻衝出黎「執法」。趁抗議者同記者齊哂人，係鏡頭面前高調「做野」，一洗「唔做野」既形象。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">帶領輿論，追究警黑合作</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">假車牌、玩煙花、南亞人；事件明顯係有組織既行動。究竟乜野人策劃？放煙花對乜野人最有利？只要扣連係警黑合作既脈絡下思考，答案根本好明顯。但我地需要既，係將依件事分析比大眾知道，唔可以比「民意翻盤」依件事發生。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見無人另外開post所以先開<br />\n如果格離有就由得呢佢沈啦"},{"pid":"edb212b2bab422a828d4032828efc1c7e5a34137","tid":1389169,"uid":8841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:54:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"591b4550687f97c988bc2cc3235777b55651cc77","tid":1389169,"uid":8841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:54:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光</span></span>"},{"pid":"d4cd4ed08dfb4f97c532cf176dbb2bc17eaa11a5","tid":1389169,"uid":8841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:55:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">復</span></span>"},{"pid":"8f32cb60aa795fe8e9fcc45b72ac713238bef9be","tid":1389169,"uid":8841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:55:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香</span></span>"},{"pid":"c1a70ac278577d9f9ffadc7a664952c6d7866da8","tid":1389169,"uid":8841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:55:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港</span></span>"},{"pid":"a0e6f6c1e8ccd363b08769593f1745ed5294c4ac","tid":1389169,"uid":8841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:55:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時</span></span>"},{"pid":"e55c6cd843dc94de669e75b1a38f9c4256bd1433","tid":1389169,"uid":8841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:56:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">代</span></span>"},{"pid":"92eb21ee10a3edf4d255ebe49f84d7b45293919a","tid":1389169,"uid":8841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:56:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革</span></span>"},{"pid":"fdbe112d19e557d58a51f0667ce56cdb78fb21ae","tid":1389169,"uid":8841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:56:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">命</span></span>"}]}